    • updateMoneyAvailable

      public void updateMoneyAvailable(boolean isIncrease, double amount)
      Updates the moneyAvailable. Adds the "amount" value if isIncrease is True, and subtracts the "amount" value if isIncrease is false as it would then be a withdrawl.
      Parameters:
      isIncrease - boolean value, true if the money is being deposited in the account.
      amount - the amount the money available goes up or down

    • updateCarsPurchased

      public void updateCarsPurchased(boolean isIncrease, int amount)
      Updates the carsPurchased. Adds the "amount" value if isIncrease is True, and subtracts the "amount" value if isIncrease is false as it would then be a decrease.
      Parameters:
      isIncrease - boolean value, true if the number of carsPurchased is increasing.
      amount - the amount the carsPurchased is being increased or decreased by.
